              <p class="text-muted-foreground text-center mb-4">
                Add your bio, expertise areas, service locations, and client list. The more
                complete, the better!
              </p>
              <div class="text-center">
                <a href="/dashboard/profile" class="text-sm text-texas-gold-500 hover:underline font-medium">
                  Profile tips →
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

